        <Parent_String>Larix (genus) [300343648], Pinaceae (family) [300343672], Pinales (order) [300343666], Pinopsida (class) [300343663], Coniferophyta (division) [300265702], Plantae (kingdom) [300132360], Eukaryota (domain) [300265677], living organisms (entities) [300390503], Living Organisms (hierarchy name) [300265673], Agents Facet [300264089]</Parent_String>
